## FORMULATION DETAIL VIEW (selectedFormulation !== null)

Show when any formulation is clicked (from dashboard, vault, or notifications).

Look up the formulation from FORMULATIONS by id.

**Header:**
- "← Back" button (clears selectedFormulation, returns to previous subView)
- Name in serif font (24px)
- "Documented {date} · 🔒 Private"

