**Ingredients:** List, each with:
- Local name (bold)
- English name
- Botanical name (italic, muted)

**Preparation:**
- Text description
- "🎤 Play original voice recording" button → shows a fake waveform (CSS bars animating) when clicked, with a "Playing... 1:12" label. Click again to "stop".

**Dosing:** Text

**Warnings:** Terra/red tag pills with ⚠️

**Expected outcome:**
- Timeline badge: "⏱️ {timeline}"
- Success indicator tags (green pills)

**📊 Outcomes section:**
- Large effectiveness % (48px, serif, green)
